    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in wonderful shape! It runs smoothly, looks great, and has plenty of life left in it. Perfect for weekend trips or just getting around town. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
