    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Experience the perfect blend of performance and luxury with this meticulously maintained vehicle. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish that still catches the light beautifully, showing only the minor, honest signs of road use expected of a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple and free of significant wear, while every dial, button, and digital display functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, this car is in its prime\u2014it has benefited from a rigorous service schedule, ensuring the engine runs smoothly and the handling remains sharp. Whether you are commuting or taking a weekend getaway, this car offers a reliable and sophisticated driving experience that stands out from the crowd. It represents an exceptional value for a driver who appreciates a car that has been treated with genuine care and is ready for the road ahead.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
