    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available for the discerning enthusiast is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies. This unit delivers a linear torque curve and an exhilarating 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated variable M differential lock. Recent technical highlights include a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to maintain structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the sharp turn-in and communicative feedback these chassis are renowned for. While displaying minor aesthetic wear consistent with its service life, its mechanical performance remains uncompromised and track-ready.",
